Recommended property `amenityFeature` is missing from `Place`.

A full example looks like this:

```
"amenityFeature": [
  {
    "name": "Changing Facilities",
    "value": true,
    "@type": "ChangingFacilities"
  },
  {
    "name": "Showers",
    "value": false,
    "@type": "Showers"
  },
  {
    "name": "Lockers",
    "value": true,
    "@type": "Lockers"
  },
  {
    "name": "Towels",
    "value": false,
    "@type": "Towels"
  },
  {
    "name": "Creche",
    "value": false,
    "@type": "Creche"
  },
  {
    "name": "Parking",
    "value": true,
    "@type": "Parking"
  }
]
```

